Cube.Name: SALES_CUBE

DerivedMeasure.Name: SALES_YTD
DerivedMeasure.MeasureExpression: SUM(SALES_CUBE.SALES) OVER (HIERARCHY "TIME".CALENDAR BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT MEMBER WITHIN ANCESTOR AT DIMENSION LEVEL "TIME".CALENDAR_YEAR)

DerivedMeasure.Name: SALES_YTD_PY
DerivedMeasure.MeasureExpression: LAG(SALES_CUBE.SALES_YTD, 1) OVER (HIERARCHY "TIME".CALENDAR BY ANCESTOR AT DIMENSION LEVEL "TIME".CALENDAR_YEAR POSITION FROM BEGINNING)

DerivedMeasure.Name: SALES_YTD_PY_PCT_CHG
DerivedMeasure.MeasureExpression: LAG_VARIANCE_PERCENT(SALES_CUBE.SALES_YTD, 1) OVER (HIERARCHY "TIME".CALENDAR BY ANCESTOR AT DIMENSION LEVEL "TIME".CALENDAR_YEAR POSITION FROM BEGINNING)

Classification.Value: ObjectQuotedDescriptionExpression=("SALES CUBE"."sales" - "SALES CUBE"."Sales Ytd Pr Year")/ABS("SALES CUBE"."Sales Ytd Pr Year")

Description.Value: Sales Ytd Pr Yr Pct Chg
Sales Ytd Pr Yr Pct Chg
Sales Ytd Pr Yr Pct Chg

DerivedMeasure.Name: SALES_PY
DerivedMeasure.MeasureExpression: LAG(SALES_CUBE.SALES, 1) OVER HIERARCHY ("TIME".CALENDAR BY ANCESTOR AT LEVEL "TIME".CALENDAR.CALENDAR_YEAR POSITION FROM BEGINNING)

DerivedMeasure.Name: SALES_PY_PCT_CHG
DerivedMeasure.MeasureExpression: 100 * LAG_VARIANCE_PERCENT(SALES_CUBE.SALES, 1) OVER HIERARCHY ("TIME".CALENDAR BY ANCESTOR AT LEVEL "TIME".CALENDAR.CALENDAR_YEAR POSITION FROM BEGINNING)

DerivedMeasure.Name: SALES_RANK_PROD_LVL
DerivedMeasure.MeasureExpression: RANK() OVER HIERARCHY (PRODUCT.STANDARD ORDER BY SALES_CUBE.SALES DESC NULLS LAST WITHIN LEVEL)

DerivedMeasure.Name: SALES_RANK_PROD_PRNT
DerivedMeasure.MeasureExpression: RANK() OVER HIERARCHY (PRODUCT.STANDARD ORDER BY SALES_CUBE.SALES DESC NULLS LAST WITHIN PARENT)

DerivedMeasure.Name: HOW_IS_SALES_YTD
DerivedMeasure.MeasureExpression: CASE WHEN SALES_CUBE.SALES_YTD_PY_PCT_CHG < 0 THEN 'Needs Improvement' WHEN SALES_CUBE.SALES_YTD_PY_PCT_CHG > 15 THEN 'Outstanding' ELSE 'On track' END

AWCubeOrganization.DefaultBuild: BUILD SPEC LOAD_AND_AGGREGATE ( LOAD NO SYNCH, SOLVE )

Cube.ConsistentSolve: SOLVE ( SUM MAINTAIN COUNT OVER ALL )
